  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599378944861-QC28YSPPEJYBCVIGPUS1/20a-20131129-135025.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>1. We think Jack's pretty darn cute &amp; if you do too, <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1iVAqFM\">please vote for him in this contest</a> for a local store called The Pump Station. It just takes a second and we would so appreciate it!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599378963837-JNLPOLTI4ZWZ5LE5530U/20b-Amy_Tan_Embroidery_Set-600x482.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>2. It's <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/black-friday?aff=6cc2c70f\">Black Friday online at Studio Calico</a>. Grab some really great products at amazing prices. For those who missed out on this <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/shop/black-friday/amy-tan-embroidery-stencil-kit?aff=6cc2c70f\">exclusive embroidery stencil kit</a>, you can grab it now for just $2.99. Sale ends Saturday 12AM EST.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599379001473-HQCWAN3D7BRSN07802PU/20c-mommasgonecity-600x427.png\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>3. I am absolutely crazy about this (new to me) Instagram account, <a href=\"http://instagram.com/mommasgonecity#\">mommasgonecity</a>. I mean, is there anything better than puppies and babies together?! I think not.</p><p>4. I've been saying the serenity prayer on a daily basis (sometimes multiple times a day). \"God grant me the serenity to accept the things I cannot change; the courage to change the things I can; and the wisdom to know the difference.\" Also I've been trying to remember to pause and take deep breaths. Just did it now, and you should try it too. ;)</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599379052649-B162WUKR733H7GWH8PNV/20d-black-friday-blogger-button.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>5. Silhouette is having a HUGE holiday sale! Visit <a href=\"http://www.silhouetteamerica.com/black\">Silhouette</a> and enter the code TANGERINE for these amazing offers valid through December 8.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
